Package com.chute.sdk.v2.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountStore  
    AccountStore.AuthConstants  
    AlbumModel
    Albums represent a collection of assets which can be created by a single user, viewed by everyone or privileged users.
    ApiLimitsModel
    The ApiLimitsModel class wraps up information regarding limit for calls to the REST API.
    AssetModel
    An asset represents a single media item and all information connected to it, viewed by everyone or privileged users.
    CommentModel
    Comments offer the ability for users to interact and comment on assets inside an album.
    CounterModel
    The CounterModel class wraps information regarding number of photo, video and inbox items for an asset or album.
    DimensionsModel
    The DimensionsModel class contains information regarding dimensions of an asset.
    FlagModel
    The FlagModel class represents a concept of asset flag.
    GeoLocationModel
    This class holds GeoLocation information connected to an asset.
    HeartModel
    The HeartModel class represents a concept of asset heart.
    LinkInfoModel
    This class holds information regarding the links contained in the LinkModel.
    LinkModel
    The LinkModel class holds self, asset and exif links.
    PaginationModel
    The PaginationModel class wraps up information about pagination of the response.
    ParcelModel
    Parcels represent a group of assets.
    ProfileModel  
    ResponseStatusModel
    The ResponseStatusModel class represents the status of the response.
    SourceCountModel
    The SourceCountModel class contains information for imported and uploaded assets to a source destination.
    SourceModel
    The SourceModel class holds asset source information such as source URL, service, import URL and original URL.
    StatsModel
    The StatsModel class holds information regarding number of uploaded and imported assets to a specific source destination made by the user.
    TestClass  
    UserCountModel
    The UserCountModel wraps information concerning number of uploaded or imported assets by a specific user.
    UserModel
    The UserModel class contains user features such as: links, name, username and avatar URL.
    VoteModel
    The VoteModel class represents a concept of asset vote.
